race.comment: TIPSY ETHICS (1) had been in super honest form hitting the frame five times on end before finishing fourth (20.17) at Gunnedah last time. Has ability and can bounce back. NEW JACK (7) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten second (22.88) in a Grade 5 at this track last time out. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. CAWBOURNE SPADE (6) was never in contention last time at this track, but prior to that won by a nose at this track (22.56) beating Isle Of Rose in a Mix 2/3 on October 28. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Has ability and is one of the better chances. NUKKUNYA (2) has claims again if she runs up to the latest effort.
